title: ESU Women's Tennis Falls to USciences, 7-2 (East Stroudsburg University Athletics)
text: ( Source : East Stroudsburg University Athletics ) STROUDSBURG - Freshman Morgan Buchter won a third-set tiebreaker at No. 4 singles and junior Kayla Loar won 6-4 , 6-4 at No. 5 singles, but East Stroudsburg University fell to USciences, 7-2,
